Table.name: LAND_RIGHT
Table.commentInRDBMS: LAND RIGHT: Describes the right to land, either the surface and/ or the mineral rights (track using LAND RIGHT CATEGORY). Land rights may be owned outright (Certificate of Title) or leased through an agreement. Agreements may be either primary (made directly with lessor) or secondary (made with other lessees). Relationships between land rights are found in LR XREF.
